<I><B><H1> AWARDS </H1> </I></B>
</FONT>

<BODY> <CENTER> <IMG src = "http://www.globalschoolsfoundation.org/Portals/2/images/Global-School-Awards.jpg"> </CENTER>

<P> <FONT SIZE = 5 COLOR = "Teal">
<B>At GIIS, an indication that we’re succeeding at what we do is ample recognition by coveted national
 and international organisations including Asia Pacific Quality Organisation, Institute of Directors, 
Spring Singapore, and Indian Merchants Chamber among many others.</B>
<BR><BR>
Since our founding in 2002, we have been committed to providing comprehensive educational opportunities
 to our students. Towards this end, we have undertaken conscious steps to instill efficiency and 
effectiveness across all our operations, including management processes, operational methodologies,
 and curriculum delivery.

The ultimate result? Not only have we created and fostered a process-driven culture, but we’ve
 also been able to synchronise and replicate these strong, benchmarked practices across all of
 our campuses.

It’s particularly significant as well as gratifying to all members of the GIIS community
 -- including management, staff, parents, and students alike -- to be honoured for our collective
 and ongoing efforts.

Our dedication to a well-rounded and holistic approach for nurturing young minds for a better tomorrow
 is no better signified than by the fact that we have been honoured with several national and 
international awards for innovation and excellence in school education in such a short period of time.

</FONT> </P>

